data.title: Olainfarm Announces €100m Investment For Ten Products Every Year
data.meta_description: Olainfarm has announced plans to find €100m in funding – including through increased efficiencies and reinvestment of profits – to invest in a five-year plan that will see it develop ten new products each year as part of efforts to become one of the top ten pharma players in Central and Eastern Europe.
